narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Alfa Development Inc. is a In Home Supportive Care provider based in Newfoundland, NJ. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $96.6M in Medicaid payments across 230K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $96.6M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
